<p><span style='color: #ff0000;'>(註2)</span>：<span style='text-decoration: underline;'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'><a href='./images/ff5_enemy_list/245.png' target='_blank'><span style='color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;'>245-塞壬</span></a></span></span> 會切換狀態，在不死系狀態才有弱點<span style='color: #ff0000;'>火與治療</span></p>
